content: The Questionnaire track kick off meeting will be on 1/4, 4p.m.-5p.m. U.S. Central Time (GMT-6).
Update. I just learned the kick-off meeting will not be through Whova. Link TBD.
Reminder: The Questionnaire track kick-off meeting is today, 4 p.m. - 5 p.m. US Central Time (GMT-6). The link is https://hl7-org.zoom.us/j/92101462635?pwd=VVQvaEMydG04R1FZeXlyZUJlN3FaUT09

A correction to what I said in the kick-off meeting: The first Questionnaire track meeting (welcome session) is 8 a.m. (U.S. Central Time) Tuesday, not 9. (I accidentally had the Whova page set to "local" time).
